reviewText: I remember watching this as a kid and I absolutely love it! It was so much fun to sing and dance to. I have a little one on the way, so when he is born, I am going to play this for him too!!!!
This is a great movie for young children. They learn the songs quick and like to sing along. I recommend this to all parents.

My nephew loved this tape when he was a child. My son watched it at my parents house and fell in love with it too. It was really hard to find because my nephew is 16 now and I think it was new when he was a baby, but had to order one for my child. It has classic kids songs like old mcdonald, yankie doodle, BINGO the dog and many other cute songs!! Highly recomend.

I received the VHS tape within reasonable time and am enjoying and remembering how much my grandson loved it when he was a tyke.  I also ordered another one from another seller and sent to him.  Thanks.

My 18 month old loves this movie so much that she has watched it till it did not work anymore.  She runs around the house saying, "boogie woogie, boogie woogie"!  She does not understand that boogie woogie has left our home.  We are from Canada and the only places we have found this tape are at garage sales...  If you have the tape hang on tight to it because they are so hard to find. Great video!!!!!
